data.description: Step into a two story dream home in Layton Lakes. The well-designed living spaces features 5 bedrooms + Loft Area, 3 bath, 3 car garage. Spacious Great Room, Open Kitchen includes plenty of cabinets, granite counters, Center Island, huge walk in Pantry, Gas Stainless appliances with a great bar area. Large Primary suite, Primary bathroom with double sinks, walk-in shower and walk-in closet. Bedrooms 3 & 4 with Jack and Jill bath. Additional Bedroom and Full Bath Downstairs.  Easy to maintain desert front,  The backyard paradise was made for entertaining with a large covered patio, synthetic grass area, fire pit and pergola. Close to shopping & restaurants.
